    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Dissolve your <strong>beef stock mix </strong>and<strong> tomato paste </strong>in 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [200ml] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p>",
