            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a high heat and once hot, add your <strong>lean</strong> <strong>beef mince</strong> with your <strong>ground</strong> <strong>smoked paprika</strong>,<strong> ground cumin</strong>, <strong>ground coriander</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to brown, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p>",
