      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once browned, add the<strong> onion petals </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until softened</p><p>Once softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 6,
