        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, reduce the heat to medium-high and add the <strong>tomato stock </strong>to the pan with a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Cook for a further 2-3 min or until the sauce has reduced and the beef mince is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>lean</strong> <strong>beef taco mix</strong></p><p>Meanwhile, add your<strong> tortillas</strong> to a plate and pop in the <strong>microwave</strong> for 20 secs on high or until warmed through</p>",
