    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the <strong>lean</strong> <strong>beef taco mix</strong> equally between each <strong>warmed tortilla </strong>and top with the <strong>charred pepper & coriander salsa</strong></p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Tip: Cooking for kids? Leave the salsa and serve the reserved chopped tomato in the tacos with the pepper strips to the side!</span></strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
